      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――『LizNoir・BIG4までの軌跡』撮影後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "— After filming “LizNoir: The Path to the BIG4”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "この間のドキュメンタリー番組\nいい仕上がりになりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That documentary program the other day\nturned out really well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "懐かしい映像が一杯ね。……あっ\nこれ、愛とこころが加入後、初のステージでの挨拶よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s so much nostalgic footage… Ah.\nThis is Ai and Kokoro’s first stage greeting after joining.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.7412923813
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "見て、{user}さん。二人ともこんなに\n緊張して……ふふ、初々しいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ {user}-san. The two of them are so\nnervous… fufu‚ they look so fresh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.8615641277,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵のデビューライブの映像もありますね\nこれは凄く貴重ですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s also footage of your debut live with Aoi‚ Rio-san.\nThis is really valuable.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 30.2912921268
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "そっ、それは観なくていいから！\n恥ずかしいじゃない！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you don’t have to watch that!\nIt’s embarrassing!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.7983663877,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "昔の自分を見ると、今ならもっと上手にやれるのに\n……って、思ってしまうわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I watch my old self‚ I think I could do it much better now…\n…that’s what I end up thinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6650330544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6483635582
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そこまで言うなら、無理に出さなくても良かったのに\nどうして公開をOKしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you feel that strongly‚ you didn’t have to release it.\nWhy did you agree to make it public?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "……そういう未熟なところも含めて、今の神崎莉央が\n――今のLizNoirがあるんじゃない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Because even those immature parts are what made Rio Kanzaki who she is today—\n—and the current LizNoir came to be.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.7766632081,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.7766632081
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "だから、どんなに恥ずかしくても、隠したりはしないわ\n……でも、わざわざ今ここで観なくてもいいでしょ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So no matter how embarrassing it is‚ I won’t try to hide it.\n…But we don’t have to watch it right here and now‚ do we!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.8433326722,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 65.136529064
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません、当時の莉央さんにも、アイドルとして\n今とはまた違う、初々しい魅力が詰まっていたので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. Even back then‚ Rio-san had\na kind of fresh idol charm that’s different from now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "分かったわよ分かったからもう勘弁してちょうだい……\n……あっ、これは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ alright‚ I get it‚ so please spare me…\n…Ah‚ this is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4107700667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "私達の初のワンマンライブの映像ね\nほら、こないだ貴方に話した、喧嘩した後のライブよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Footage from our first solo live.\nYou know‚ the one I told you about—the live after we had that fight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、莉央さんと葵が喧嘩をした後\n莉央さんが大人になって許してあげた話ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ the one after you and Aoi argued—\nwhen you were the mature one and forgave her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……そ、そうね。そんな話だったわね……！\nそれで、実はライブ直前に、また葵が不機嫌になったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? …Y-yes‚ that’s how the story went…!\nActually‚ right before the live‚ Aoi got upset again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.8601801238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "不機嫌？　本番ではこんなにいい表情をしてるのに？\n一体、ライブの直前に何があったんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Upset? Even though she looks so good on stage?\nWhat happened right before the live?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.0531706332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "あの子ったら、本番直前になって\nまた文句を言い出したの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That girl‚ right before the show‚\nstarted complaining again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5401776316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "もっと自由に踊りたいとか\nこういうのは僕の趣味じゃないとか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Saying she wanted to dance more freely‚\nthat this kind of thing wasn’t her taste…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.1068442983,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私は大人だったから怒らなかったわ\nかわりに、こうしてやったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I was the mature one‚ so I didn’t get angry.\nInstead‚ I did this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.7735109649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.7735109649
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと……近いですよ。何をする気ですか？\n……うわっ！　俺の頬をつままないで下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait… you’re too close. What are you doing?\nWhoa! Don’t pinch my cheek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 148.3978640395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "こんな感じに、葵の頬をむぎゅってしてあげたの\n……自分でやってなんだけど、少し照れるわね、これ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I squished Aoi’s cheeks like this.\n…Even though I did it myself‚ it’s a little embarrassing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0591569585,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.9187260785
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう分かりましたから\n俺で実演するのは止めて下さいよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-okay‚ I get it now.\nPlease stop demonstrating it on me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 165.7767988997
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "そう？　じゃ、話を戻すわね。……それで葵に言ったの\n「そんな表情じゃ、可愛い顔が台無しよ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Then let’s get back to the story… I told Aoi‚\n“With that expression‚ your cute face is going to waste.”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.4340321543,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "その一言で、葵の機嫌が直ったんですか？\nその上、本番であんないい表情を見せるなんて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did that one line fix her mood?\nAnd then she gave such a great expression on stage…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.6067533332
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio015.m4a",
      "text": "機嫌が直ったかどうかは、分からないわ\n顔を背けられちゃったから。でも効果はあったみたいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t know if her mood improved.\nShe turned her face away. But it seemed to work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.6074558578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 195.3289528051
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio016.m4a",
      "text": "……あの頃、葵は葵で、私とのコミュニケーションに\n悩んでいたんだと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Back then‚ I think Aoi had her own struggles too\nwith how to communicate with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.7407891912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
