      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_12_03-rio020.m4a",
      "text": "分かってるわ。……それにしても、考えたわね\nドキュメンタリーの放送が終わったと思ったら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know. Still… you really planned this out.\nJust when the documentary ends‚",
