      "text": "だから同じ曲と衣装――同じ条件で、過去の莉央さんと\n現在の莉央さんを見比べられたら、素敵だと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So with the same song and outfits—the same conditions—\nI thought it’d be nice to compare the past Rio-san with the present one.",
