      "text": "そう聞こえた？　逆よ、むしろ……\n私達がどれだけ成長したか見せつける、いい機会だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did it sound that way? It’s the opposite. In fact…\nit’s a perfect chance to show how much we’ve grown.",
